{"prompt": "Develop an elegant online presence for a high-end beauty salon. The primary color should be a serene lavender.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elysian Beauty Lounge</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            background-color: #f8f0f8; /* A very light lavender background */\n            color: #4a3e4e; /* Deep lavender text */\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0b0ff, #c8a2c8); /* Lavender gradient */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            color: #8a55a3; /* Medium lavender for headings */\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #c8a2c8;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 3rem 5%;\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n        }\n        #services ul, #gallery ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        #services li, .gallery-item {\n            background-color: #f0e8f0; /* Very light purple accent */\n            padding: 20px